### Glossary

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Term | Definition |
| Agent | An AI agent definition (JSON config + MD prompt) that performs a specific SDLC role |
| Steering | Workspace-level rules that guide agent behavior across all interactions |
| Hook | An automated trigger that fires on file system events |
| Template | A markdown document template with placeholders for agent-generated content |
| Injection | The process of copying bundled resources into a target workspace |
| Manifest | The .sdlc-checksums.json file containing SHA-256 hashes of all bundled files |

